    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在 GTR - Garage Town Racing 的世界中建造、管理和竞速</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034980/extras/d07eee00ca39c40b97780b9d880c6958.avif?t=1753302362\" width=630 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <i><strong>GTR - Garage Town Racing</strong></i> 中掌控您的车库，在这里，您不仅仅是一名车手！这款管理和赛车游戏让您定制和增强车间和汽车的每一个细节。收集独特的车辆，从头打造模型，并在 PvP 竞赛中与朋友一较高下！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>GTR - Garage Town Racing</strong></i> 将赛车的肾上腺素与管理策略结合，玩家有机会将一个小车库变成汽车爱好者聚集的城市中心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034980/extras/c6f1a23dd82ae8d839bb6dde4f3eb6d3.avif?t=1753302362\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034980/extras_big/c6f1a23dd82ae8d839bb6dde4f3eb6d3.avif?t=1753302362 width=800 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特点</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扩展并升级您的工作空间，吸引更多客户并增加利润，将您的车库打造成真正的强大中心。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在实时挑战中与朋友竞技，证明您的车库能打造出城市最好的汽车。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034980/extras/2ad8069a4c096bea1cdf14de63905634.avif?t=1753302362\" width=630 height=122 /></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >定制汽车的每一个细节，从引擎到喷漆。装饰您的车库，吸引新客户。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034980/extras/0f63ed68fa1db5fdabbff44d3d9254dc.avif?t=1753302362\" width=630 height=122 /></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找独特的零件，制造原创车辆，打造独一无二的汽车收藏。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034980/extras/1f1f88d9be70868dd8437ecf1e734a7d.avif?t=1753302362\" width=630 height=122 /></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >访问朋友的车库，向他们发起竞速挑战并交换稀有零件来升级您的库存。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034980/extras/c6f1a23dd82ae8d839bb6dde4f3eb6d3.avif?t=1753302362\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034980/extras_big/c6f1a23dd82ae8d839bb6dde4f3eb6d3.avif?t=1753302362 width=800 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>个性化的竞速与管理体验</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034980/extras/b3143d6afe286045f9ecd0a957951357.avif?t=1753302362\" width=630 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <i><strong>GTR - Garage Town Racing</strong></i> 中，爱车的激情远不止于赛道。定制您的每辆车，准备参加精彩的比赛，与其他玩家建立联系，将您的车库打造成独一无二的车间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果您是赛车和策略的爱好者，<i><strong>GTR - Garage Town Racing</strong></i> 提供这两者的最佳体验，在这里，您的车库是城市的中心，开放的道路是您的舞台。</p>",
